  - id: "g\xF6vdesi"
    valence: ' processus xiphoideus'
    doc_type: " han\xE7ersi \xE7\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131;\xDC\xE7 k\u0131s\u0131mdan
      olu\u015Fur. \xDCstteki k\u0131sm\u0131na sternum sap\u0131 (manubrium sterni)"
    content_type: " ortadaki k\u0131sm\u0131na sternum"
    title: 
    topic: 
    region: 
    tags: 
    body: 
    steps: 
    source: 
  - id: "g\xF6vdesi (corpus sterni) ve u\xE7 k\u0131sm\u0131na ise han\xE7ersi \xE7\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131
      (processus xiphoideus) denir.;[Manubrium sterni hem k\xF6pr\xFCc\xFCk kemi\u011Fi
      (clavicula) hem de 1 ve 2\u2019nci kaburga ile eklem yapar."
    valence: " Corpus sterni her iki taraf\u0131nda bulunan 2 ve 7\u2019nci kaburgalarla
      eklem yapar."
    doc_type: " Processus xiphoideus kaburgalarla eklem yapmaz.];Ders kitab\u0131
      s.60"
    content_type: 
    title: 
    topic: 
    region: 
