  - id: ossa_costae
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: bone
    title: Ossa Costae
    topic: Movement System
    region: Trunk
    tags: "thoracic cage; g\xF6\u011F\xFCs kafesi; ossa costae; kaburga; kosta; ger\xE7ek
      kaburga; yalanc\u0131 kaburga; y\xFCzen kaburga"
    body: "Ba\u015F k\u0131s\u0131mlar\u0131 (caput costae) arkada g\xF6\u011F\xFCs
      omurlar\u0131yla eklem yapar. Kaburgalar sternuma ba\u011Flanma \xF6zelliklerine
      g\xF6re iki gruba ayr\u0131l\u0131r. Sternumla do\u011Frudan eklem yapan ilk
      7 \xE7ift kaburgaya ger\xE7ek kaburga denir. Son 5 \xE7ift kaburgaya ise yalanc\u0131
      kaburga denir. Yalanc\u0131 kaburgalar\u0131n ilk 3 \xE7iftinin (8"
    steps: " 9 ve 10\u2019uncu) k\u0131k\u0131rdaklar\u0131 \xF6nce kendi aralar\u0131nda
      birle\u015Fip 7\u2019nci kaburgan\u0131n k\u0131k\u0131rda\u011F\u0131na kat\u0131l\u0131r
      ve sternumla dolayl\u0131 eklem yapar. Son 2 \xE7ift yalanc\u0131 kaburga (11
      ve 12\u2019nci) kaslar\u0131n i\xE7inde serbest olarak sonlan\u0131r ve y\xFCzen
      kaburga olarak adland\u0131r\u0131l\u0131r."
    source: 
  - id: os_clavicula
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: bone
    title: Os Clavicula
    topic: Movement System
    region: Upper_Extremity
    tags: "cingulum membri superioris; omuz; k\xF6pr\xFCc\xFCk kemi\u011Fi; k\xF6pr\xFC"
    body: "Her iki omzun \xF6n taraf\u0131nda hem k\xFCrek kemi\u011Fi hem de sternum
      ile eklem yapar. V\xFCcutta en s\u0131k k\u0131r\u0131lan"
    steps: 
    source: 
  - id: "kemiktir. Omuzla g\xF6\u011F\xFCs aras\u0131nda k\xF6pr\xFC g\xF6revi yapar.
      Kemikle\u015Fmeye ilk ba\u015Flayan kemiktir.;;Ders kitab\u0131 s.61"
    valence: 
    doc_type: 
    content_type: 
    title: 
    topic: 
    region: 
    tags: 
    body: 
    steps: 
    source: 
  - id: os_scapula
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: bone
    title: Os Scapula
    topic: Movement System
    region: Upper_Extremity
    tags: "cingulum membri superioris; omuz; k\xFCrek kemi\u011Fi; acromion; korakoid
      \xE7\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131; processus coracoideus; glenoid \xE7ukur; cavitas
      glenoidalis"
    body: "Her iki omzun arka b\xF6lgesinde T2-T7 aras\u0131nda yer al\u0131r. Arkadan
      d\u0131\u015F yana do\u011Fru uzanan \xE7\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131s\u0131na acromion
      denir. Acromion \xE7\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131s\u0131 k\xF6pr\xFCc\xFCk kemi\u011Fi
      ile eklem yapar. \xDCst d\u0131\u015F yanda \xF6ne do\u011Fru uzanan ve baz\u0131
      kaslar\u0131n tutundu\u011Fu gagaya benzer \xE7\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131s\u0131na
      korakoid \xE7\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131 (processus coracoideus) denir. \xDCst d\u0131\u015F
      kenar\u0131nda ise kol kemi\u011Fiyle eklem yapan glenoid \xE7ukur (cavitas
      glenoidalis) bulunur."
    steps: 
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.61"
  - id: os_humerus
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: bone
    title: Os Humerus
    topic: Movement System
    region: Upper_Extremity
    tags: "brachium; kol; kol kemi\u011Fi; uzun; caput humeri; humerus ba\u015F\u0131;
      trochlea humeri; humerus makaras\u0131; capitulum humeri; humerus ba\u015F\xE7\u0131\u011F\u0131"
    body: "Omuz ve dirsek eklemi aras\u0131nda bulunan kemiktir. Humerus ba\u015F\u0131
      (caput humeri)"
    steps: " k\xFCrek kemi\u011Fi ile eklem (omuz eklemi) yapar. Alt ucu iki \xF6n
      kol kemi\u011Fi ile eklem (dirsek eklemi) yapar. \u0130\xE7 yandaki dirsek
      kemi\u011Fi ile eklem yapan k\u0131sm\u0131na humerus makaras\u0131 (trochlea
      humeri) ve d\u0131\u015F yandaki d\xF6ner kemikle eklem yapan k\u0131sm\u0131na
      humerus ba\u015F\xE7\u0131\u011F\u0131 (capitulum humeri) denir."
    source: "[\"\xDCst ekstremitenin en uzun kemi\u011Fidir.\"]"
  - id: os_ulna
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: bone
    title: Os Ulna
    topic: Movement System
    region: Upper_Extremity
    tags: "antebrachium; \xF6n kol; dirsek kemi\u011Fi; olecranon; dirsek \xE7\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131s\u0131;
      caput ulnae; ulna ba\u015F\u0131; ser\xE7e parmak"
    body: "Ser\xE7e parmak taraf\u0131ndaki kemiktir. Humerus ile eklem yapan \xFCst
      ucuna olecranon (dirsek \xE7\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131s\u0131) denir. Ulna ba\u015F\u0131
      (caput ulnae) a\u015Fa\u011F\u0131da olup bilek eklemine kat\u0131l\u0131r."
    steps: 
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.62"
  - id: os_radius
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: bone
    title: Os Radius
    topic: Movement System
    region: Upper_Extremity
    tags: "antebrachium; \xF6n kol; d\xF6ner kemik; caput radii; radius ba\u015F\u0131;
      ba\u015Fparmak"
    body: "Ba\u015Fparmak taraf\u0131ndaki kemiktir. \xDCstteki radius ba\u015F\u0131
      (caput radii) humerus ile eklem yapar. Anatomik duru\u015Fta ulna ile paraleldir.
      \xD6ne uzat\u0131lan elin avu\xE7 i\xE7i a\u015Fa\u011F\u0131 \xE7evrildi\u011Finde
      bu kemik ulnan\u0131n \xFCzerine do\u011Fru d\xF6ner. Alt ucu bilek eklemine
      kat\u0131l\u0131r."
    steps: 
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.62"
  - id: ossa_carpi
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: bone
    title: Ossa Carpi
    topic: Movement System
    region: Upper_Extremity
    tags: "manus; el; bilek; el bile\u011Fi"
    body: "El bile\u011Finde 4\u2019erli iki s\u0131ra halinde 8 k\u0131sa kemik
      bulunur. \xD6n kol kemikleri ile el tara\u011F\u0131 kemikleri aras\u0131nda
      yer al\u0131r. Kaslar ve ba\u011Flarla birbirine s\u0131k\u0131ca ba\u011Fland\u0131klar\u0131
      i\xE7in hareketleri k\u0131s\u0131tl\u0131d\u0131r."
    steps: 
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.63"
  - id: ossa_metacarpi
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: bone
    title: Ossa Metacarpi
    topic: Movement System
    region: Upper_Extremity
    tags: manus; el; tarak; el tarak
    body: "Avu\xE7 i\xE7i ve el s\u0131rt\u0131n\u0131n iskeletini olu\u015Fturan
      5 uzun kemiktir. El bile\u011Fi kemikleri ile parmak kemikleri aras\u0131nda
      bulunur."
    steps: 
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.63"
  - id: ossa_digitorum_manus
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: bone
    title: Ossa Digitorum Manus (Phalanges)
    topic: Movement System
    region: Upper_Extremity
    tags: manus; el; parmak; el parmak
    body: "Be\u015F parmakta toplam 14 kemik bulunur. Kemik say\u0131s\u0131 ba\u015Fparmakta
      2 di\u011Fer parmaklarda 3\u2019er tanedir."
    steps: 
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.63"
  - id: os_coxa
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: bone
    title: Os Coxa
    topic: Movement System
    region: Lower_Extremity
    tags: "alt ekstremite; kal\xE7a; pelvis; \xE7ift; d\xFCzensiz; acetabulum"
    body: "Pelvisin yan duvar\u0131n\u0131 olu\u015Fturan ve uyluk kemi\u011Fi ile
      eklem yapan kal\xE7a kemi\u011Fidir."
    steps: "[\"D\u0131\u015F y\xFCz\xFCnde femur ile eklem yapan \xE7anak \u015Feklinde
      acetabulum bulunur.\", \"Sa\u011F ve sol olmak \xFCzere 2 adet os coxae vard\u0131r.\",
      \"Sakrum ile birlikte pelvis bo\u015Flu\u011Funu olu\u015Fturur.\", \"\xDC\xE7
      kemi\u011Fin birle\u015Fmesiyle olu\u015Fur.\", \"15\u201316 ya\u015Flar\u0131nda
      kayna\u015Farak tek kemik haline gelir.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.64"
