  - id: syndesmosis
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: Joint
    title: Syndesmosis
    topic: Movement System
    region: Joints
    tags: eklem; oynamaz; fibroz; syndesmosis
    body: "Kemik y\xFCzlerinin birbirine ligamentlerle ba\u011Fland\u0131\u011F\u0131
      oynamaz eklemdir."
    steps: "[\"Kemik y\xFCzleri birbirine ligamentlerle s\u0131k\u0131ca ba\u011Flanm\u0131\u015Ft\u0131r.\",
      \"\xD6rnek: Ulna ile radius aras\u0131ndaki eklem.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.67"
  - id: synchondrosis
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: Joint
    title: Synchondrosis
    topic: Movement System
    region: Joints
    tags: "eklem; yar\u0131 oynar; synchondrosis; kartilaginoz; hiyalin k\u0131k\u0131rdak;
      sternum; kosta; epifiz plak"
    body: "Eklem y\xFCzleri aras\u0131nda hiyalin k\u0131k\u0131rdak bulunan yar\u0131
      oynar eklemdir."
    steps: "[\"\xD6rnek: Kaburgalar ile sternum aras\u0131ndaki eklemler.\", \"\xD6rnek:
      Uzun kemiklerin epifiz plaklar\u0131.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.67"
  - id: symphysis
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: Joint
    title: Symphysis
    topic: Movement System
    region: Joints
    tags: "eklem; yar\u0131 oynar; kartilaginoz; fibroz k\u0131k\u0131rdak; disk;
      pelvis; omur"
    body: "Eklem y\xFCzleri aras\u0131nda fibroz k\u0131k\u0131rdak yap\u0131s\u0131nda
      disk bulunan yar\u0131 oynar eklemdir."
    steps: "[\"\xD6rnek: Pubis kemikleri aras\u0131ndaki eklem (symphysis pubis).\",
      \"\xD6rnek: Omurlar aras\u0131ndaki eklemler (symphysis intervertebralis).\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.67"
  - id: art_temporomandibularis
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: Joint
    title: Art. Temporomandibularis
    topic: Movement System
    region: Joints
    tags: "eklem; oynar; temporomandibular; \xE7ene; kafa"
    body: "Kafa b\xF6lgesinin tek oynar eklemidir."
    steps: "[\"Temporal ve mandibular kemik aras\u0131nda bulunur.\", \"Alt \xE7eneyi
      d\u0131\u015F yana, i\xE7 yana, \xF6ne ve arkaya do\u011Fru hareket ettirir.\",
      \"Alt \xE7eneyi yukar\u0131 ve a\u015Fa\u011F\u0131 do\u011Fru hareket ettirir.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.70"
  - id: art_atlantooccipitalis
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: Joint
    title: Art. Atlantooccipitalis
    topic: Movement System
    region: Joints
    tags: eklem; oynar; atlantooccipital; atlas; oksipital
    body: "Oksipital kemik ile atlas aras\u0131ndaki oynar eklemdir."
    steps: "[\"Ba\u015Fa fleksiyon, ekstansiyon ve biraz da lateral fleksiyon yapt\u0131r\u0131r.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.70"
  - id: art_atlantoaxialis
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: Joint
    title: Art. Atlantoaxialis
    topic: Movement System
    region: Joints
    tags: eklem; oynar; atlantoaxial; atlas; eksen
    body: "Atlas ile eksen aras\u0131ndaki oynar eklemdir."
    steps: "[\"Ba\u015Fa rotasyon hareketi yapt\u0131r\u0131r.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.70"
  - id: art_humeri
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: Joint
    title: Art. Humeri
    topic: Movement System
    region: Joints
    tags: eklem; oynar; omuz; humerus; skapula
    body: "Humerus ba\u015F\u0131 ile skapula kemi\u011Fi aras\u0131ndaki oynar eklemdir."
    steps: "[\"V\xFCcudun en fazla hareket yetene\u011Fine sahip eklemidir.\",  \"Kola
      t\xFCm hareketleri yapt\u0131r\u0131r.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.70"
  - id: art_cubiti
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: Joint
    title: Art. Cubiti
    topic: Movement System
    region: Joints
    tags: eklem; oynar; dirsek; humerus; ulna; radius
    body: Humerus
    steps: " ulna ve radius kemikleri aras\u0131ndaki oynar eklemdir."
    source: "[\"\xDC\xE7 ayr\u0131 eklemden olu\u015Fur.\", \"Hem fleksiyon ve ekstansiyon
      hem de pronasyon ve supinasyon yapt\u0131r\u0131r.\"]"
  - id: art_ radiocarpalis
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: Joint
    title: Art. Radiocarpalis
    topic: Movement System
    region: Joints
    tags: "eklem; oynar; el bile\u011Fi; radius; karpal"
    body: "Proksimaldeki \xFC\xE7 karpal kemik ile radius kemi\u011Fi aras\u0131ndaki
      oynar eklemdir."
    steps: "[\"Ulna kemi\u011Fi bu ekleme girmez.\", \"El bile\u011Fine fleksiyon
      , ekstansiyon, abd\xFCksiyon, add\xFCksiyon, sirk\xFCmd\xFCksiyon yapt\u0131r\u0131r.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.70"
  - id: art_coxae
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: Joint
    title: Art. Coxae
    topic: Movement System
    region: Joints
    tags: "eklem; oynar; kal\xE7a; acetabulum; femur"
    body: "Kal\xE7a kemi\u011Finin acetabulum \xE7ukuru ile femur ba\u015F\u0131
      aras\u0131ndaki oynar eklemdir."
    steps: "[\"Baca\u011Fa t\xFCm hareketleri yapt\u0131r\u0131r.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.70"
  - id: art_genus
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: Joint
    title: Art. Genus
    topic: Movement System
    region: Joints
    tags: eklem; oynar; diz; femur; tibia; patella
    body: "V\xFCcudun en b\xFCy\xFCk ve karma\u015F\u0131k eklemlerinden biridir."
    steps: "[\"Femur, tibia ve patella kemikleri aras\u0131ndad\u0131r.\", \"Fibula
      kemi\u011Fi bu ekleme kat\u0131lmaz.\", \"Eklem y\xFCzleri aras\u0131nda menisk\xFCsler
      vard\u0131r.\", \"Eklem \xF6n y\xFCz\xFCnde patella bulunur.\", \"Dize fleksiyon
      ve ekstansiyon yapt\u0131r\u0131r.\", \"Yar\u0131 fleksiyonda biraz i\xE7 ve
      d\u0131\u015F rotasyon yapt\u0131r\u0131r.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.71"
